ISO 3166 Country Codes

Source: R/utils-iso-3166.R
iso_3166_codes.Rd

List all ISO 3166 2 and 3 digit Country codes.

iso_3166_codes()

Value

a data.frame

Details

Country codes provided by rust_iso3166.

Examples

head(iso_3166_codes())
#> # A data frame: 6 × 3
#>   country        code_2 code_3
#> * <chr>          <chr>  <chr> 
#> 1 Afghanistan    AF     AFG   
#> 2 Åland Islands  AX     ALA   
#> 3 Albania        AL     ALB   
#> 4 Algeria        DZ     DZA   
#> 5 American Samoa AS     ASM   
#> 6 Andorra        AD     AND
